quran[28{c,v,t}:
26,84,aur pichlle logon mein mera zikar naik ( jari ) kar
26,85,aur mujhe Nemat ki bahisht ke varson mein kar
26,86,aur mere baap ko bakhash day ke woh gumrahon mein se hai
26,87,aur jis din log utha kharray kiye jayen ge mujhe ruswa nah kejio
26,88,jis din nah maal hi kuch faida day saka ga aur nah betay
26,89,haan jo shakhs khuda ke paas pak dil le kar aaya ( woh bach jaye ga )
26,90,aur bahisht parhaiz garon ke qareeb kar di jaye gi
26,91,aur dozakh gumrahon ke samnay layi jaye gi
26,92,aur un se kaha jaye ga ke jin ko tum pujte they woh kahan hain ?
26,93,yani jin ko khuda ke siwa ( pujte they )kiya woh tumhari madad kar saktay hain ya khud badla le satke hain
26,94,to woh aur gumraah ( yani buut aur buut parast ) avndhe munh dozakh mein daal diye jayen ge
26,95,aur shetan ke lashkar sab ke sab ( daakhil jahannum hon ge )
26,96,woh aapas mein jhagrain ge aur kahin ge
26,97,ke khuda ki qasam hum to Sarih gumraahi mein they
26,98,jab ke tumhe ( khuday-e ) rab alameen ke barabar th_hrate they
26,99,aur hum ko un gunahgaaron hi ne gumraahkiya tha
26,100,to ( aaj ) nah koi hamara sifarish karne wala hai
26,101,aur nah garam josh dost
26,102,kash hamein ( duniya mein ) phir jana ho tum hum mominon mein ho jaien
26,103,be shak is mein nishani hai aur un mein aksar imaan laane walay nahi
26,104,aur tumhara perwar-digaar to ghalib aur meharban hai
26,105,qoum Nooh ne bhi payghambaroon ko jhtlaya
26,106,jab un se un ke bhai Nooh ne kaha ke tum drtay kyun nahi
26,107,mein to tumhara amanat daar hon
26,108,to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
26,109,aur is kaam ka tum se kuch sila nahi mangta. mera sila to khuday-e rab alameen hi par hai
26,110,to khuda se daro aur mere kehnay par chalo
26,111,woh bolay kekiya hum tum ko maan len aur tumahray pairo to razeel log hotay hain
